Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.09,0:00:05.76,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,Each time my heart passes by someone else,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.76,0:00:08.88,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,each time we collide,\NI had always thought
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.99,0:00:12.56,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,how it would be nice if words and feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.56,0:00:15.59,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,could portray everything that we wish for.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.13,0:00:21.87,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,But there are people with stronger wishes than words or justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.61,0:00:26.57,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,What you need is not words, but a strong heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.08,0:00:29.55,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,No lies, no hesitation...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.55,0:00:32.55,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,We will stand against those straightforward eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.55,0:00:34.48,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,with a determined heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.18,0:00:39.18,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,{\i0}Magical Girl Lyrical Nanoha A's{\i1} will now begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.59,0:00:50.59,Nanoha OP,,0,0,0,,Prayers echoing in the vast skies turn to miracles
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.21,0:01:13.55,Nanoha OP,,0,0,0,,Teardrops melt and flow into the blue of the middle of the night
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.55,0:01:19.73,Nanoha OP,,0,0,0,,I met a warmth that engulfs all without hesitation
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.73,0:01:22.76,Nanoha OP,,0,0,0,,Just like the pure white snow
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.76,0:01:25.83,Nanoha OP,,0,0,0,,Words that are honest no matter how far you go
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.83,0:01:32.71,Nanoha OP,,0,0,0,,It moves me as I wear wings of steel
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.71,0:01:38.24,Nanoha OP,,0,0,0,,Each time I am hurt,\NI can become kinder
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.24,0:01:46.68,Nanoha OP,,0,0,0,,My only wish is to protect that smile of yours to the end
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.72,0:01:53.73,Nanoha OP,,0,0,0,,Memories of sadness engraved across the ages
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.73,0:02:00.07,Nanoha OP,,0,0,0,,You are an angel of light, catching them straight on
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.07,0:02:05.87,Nanoha OP,,0,0,0,,An eternal blaze that stopped in my heart that day
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.87,0:02:09.34,Nanoha OP,,0,0,0,,Releasing the deep darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.34,0:02:15.71,Nanoha OP,,0,0,0,,It opens the door of freedom
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.71,0:02:22.64,Nanoha OP,,0,0,0,,Towards the strong, boundless future
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.75,0:02:39.69,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,That's all the data we have.\NIs it of any help?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.19,0:02:43.52,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Yes... thank you. It's a big help.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.90,0:02:48.93,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Hey, all of you are going to come over here today, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.93,0:02:51.60,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Yeah, regarding the {\i1}Arthra{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.60,0:02:54.93,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,How about we find some time and have a meal together?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.60,0:02:57.70,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,I'd like to hear about that girl, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.64,0:03:00.78,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,That girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.78,0:03:03.14,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,You know, the one you're taking care of.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.78,0:03:05.98,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,The one you said you wanted to adopt.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.98,0:03:08.65,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Oh, you mean Fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.09,0:03:12.62,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Right, Fate. Is she doing well?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.62,0:03:13.65,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.99,0:03:19.55,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,I feel bad about having her working with us on this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.16,0:03:22.73,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,But she's together with her good friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.73,0:03:24.96,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,so she looks like she's enjoying it as she works.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.93,0:03:40.97,Nanoha A's Title1,,0,0,0,,{\an5\blur0.5\frx-30\pos(476,520)}With the Broken Past and Present
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.62,0:03:49.83,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,There sure are a lot of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.83,0:03:53.23,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Well, lately all of them have similar specs.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.86,0:03:56.60,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,So I think you can choose by how it looks, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.60,0:03:59.90,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,But you still want one that has good text messaging capabilities!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.60,0:04:03.66,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,With a good, clear camera, you can have all sorts of fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.71,0:04:08.91,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,But in the end, the color and design is what's important.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.61,0:04:11.58,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Ease of use is also important!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.95,0:04:15.32,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,External memory is very useful, so it's a good thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.32,0:04:16.72,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.72,0:04:20.62,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you can keep lots of pictures and music in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.62,0:04:24.93,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,And you can attach them to your text messages to send to your friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.93,0:04:27.36,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,That's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.36,0:04:28.93,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,It's rather useful.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.33,0:04:30.30,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,{\c&HE1E1E1&}That one's nice...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.27,0:04:33.00,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.00,0:04:34.33,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Yes, thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.64,0:04:41.58,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Fate... here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.38,0:04:45.61,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much, Commodore Lindy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.72,0:04:53.72,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Sorry to make you wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.72,0:04:54.62,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.62,0:04:56.16,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Did you find a good number?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.16,0:04:57.69,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.69,0:04:58.63,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.63,0:05:01.22,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Let's see... here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.94,0:05:16.71,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,The supermassive database that has every book and piece of data imaginable
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.71,0:05:19.88,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,from every world the Bureau administrates.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.78,0:05:23.65,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Where many histories are packed whole,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.65,0:05:27.38,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,you can say it's the place that stocks memories of entire worlds.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.99,0:05:32.39,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,That is this place, the Infinity Library.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.39,0:05:36.93,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Though most of the contents are completely unorganized.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.93,0:05:39.63,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Looking for something here is a big hassle, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.24,0:05:45.11,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Usually, people form large teams and research here for years on end.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.81,0:05:49.90,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Investigating past history is what my clan does for a living.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.81,0:05:54.68,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,I brought search magic as well, so we'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.68,0:05:55.95,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.95,0:05:58.32,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,You're one of the Scrya kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.82,0:06:01.46,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Both Lotte and I have work to do,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.46,0:06:04.12,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,so we can't stay here the whole time until you're done,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.86,0:06:06.73,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,but we'll help as much as we can.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.20,0:06:10.83,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,After all, it's a request from\NChroboy, my cute apprentice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.40,0:06:18.84,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,I see... so both Alisa and Suzuka are taking violin lessons?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.84,0:06:19.91,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.91,0:06:23.91,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,They text me to tell me about their lessons all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.91,0:06:25.14,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.78,0:06:27.04,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,I'm back!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.79,0:06:39.19,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Has the captain taken off for the Main Office already?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.76,0:06:40.86,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.86,0:06:43.13,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Apparently, the weaponry refit of the {\i1}Arthra{\i0} is finished,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.13,0:06:46.40,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,so she went on a test drive with Allex and the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.90,0:06:51.03,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Weaponry... that must be the Arc-en-Ciel.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.74,0:06:55.73,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Hopefully we can get by till the end without using that scary thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.21,0:06:58.48,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Chrono isn't here, either...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.85,0:07:00.05,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,So until either of them gets back,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.05,0:07:03.12,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,looks like you're the temporary leader, Miss Amy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.12,0:07:05.11,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,So much responsibility!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.16,0:07:08.92,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,That's a scary thought in a different way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.92,0:07:13.89,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm sure there can't be that many emergencies going on...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.84,0:07:27.54,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Civilization level, zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.54,0:07:30.88,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,It's a desert world with no human inhabitants.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.45,0:07:41.41,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,At least 45 minutes to assemble agents to form a barrier...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.96,0:07:44.79,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,This isn't looking good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.37,0:07:52.50,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Amy, I'll go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.50,0:07:53.80,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.44,0:07:57.24,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Right. Please do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.81,0:07:59.54,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.88,0:08:04.08,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Nanoha, you're our back-end defense.\NStay here on standby.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.08,0:08:05.05,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.25,0:08:12.89,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Bardiche!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.89,0:08:13.91,Nanoha Device1,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.37,0:08:28.17,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Small wonder that Vita had such a hard time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.17,0:08:30.37,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,This is a slightly troublesome opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.55,0:08:40.95,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Dammit...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.19,0:08:53.53,Nanoha Device1,,0,0,0,,Thunder Blade
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.57,0:09:05.84,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Break!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.92,0:09:21.02,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Are you worried about your mistress?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.36,0:09:25.23,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,You again...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.23,0:09:27.42,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Our mistresses are one-on-one right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.96,0:09:29.26,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,The same goes for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.37,0:09:34.20,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Signum is our leader,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.20,0:09:36.00,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,but she is not my mistress.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.04,0:09:42.48,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,That means your mistress is the mistress of the Book of Darkness, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.42,0:09:54.36,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,Fate! What are you doing, helping her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.36,0:09:56.15,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,You're supposed to capture her!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.49,0:09:59.96,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, I couldn't help it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.43,0:10:02.96,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,I won't give my thanks, Testarossa.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.00,0:10:05.49,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Did I get in your way?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.40,0:10:10.31,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,You crushed our target for filling the Book.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.61,0:10:17.98,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Well, my job is to get in the way of villains.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.61,0:10:22.42,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,I see. That's right, I'm a villain.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.76,0:10:31.56,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Another location?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.03,0:10:38.10,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Is this end the real deal?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.10,0:10:39.54,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Nanoha!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.54,0:10:40.63,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.27,0:10:46.67,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,It's been a while, Commodore Lindy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.04,0:10:48.07,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.61,0:10:50.20,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,The Book of Darkness Incident...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.98,0:10:52.41,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Any progress on it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.32,0:10:57.22,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,It's quite a difficult task, but I will manage it well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.52,0:11:02.22,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,You do excellent work.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.99,0:11:06.39,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you won't make a blunder, unlike the time that I tried.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.00,0:11:11.19,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,I had mentioned this to you at my husband's funeral,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.50,0:11:15.10,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,but that blunder was not caused by you, Admiral.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.57,0:11:22.67,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,No commander could have ever predicted such a thing would happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.06,0:11:38.13,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Oh... how dextrous...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.13,0:11:40.46,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,You can figure out what's inside like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.46,0:11:44.02,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Yes... well, sort of.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.40,0:11:48.07,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Um... Miss Lieselotte, you two were there for
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.07,0:11:50.54,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,the previous Book of Darkness Incident, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.54,0:11:51.47,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.24,0:11:55.08,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,It was, after all, only eleven years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.68,0:11:58.31,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Um... is it true?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.71,0:12:02.38,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,That Chrono's father passed away in the incident...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.79,0:12:08.02,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,It's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.62,0:12:11.36,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Aria and I were together with Father,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.09,0:12:14.15,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,so we saw it really close up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.63,0:12:17.13,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,The one transporting the Book of\NDarkness that we thought was sealed
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.13,0:12:21.54,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,was Clyde... oh, that's Chrono's father.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.54,0:12:22.66,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.37,0:12:30.18,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,We saw Clyde go down with the guard ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.65,0:12:36.52,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,So the way to seal it turned out to be the Arc-en-Ciel after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.52,0:12:41.08,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,There is no other weapon that can emit so much power at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.52,0:12:44.22,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,That thing causes too much collateral damage.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.66,0:12:46.65,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,I hope we can settle everything without firing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.20,0:12:49.60,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,It would be nice if we could find its mistress.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.57,0:12:56.47,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Well, even if we got the mistress down,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.47,0:12:59.34,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,the Book of Darkness has a respawn function,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.34,0:13:03.15,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,so all we'd do is push back the problem for several years,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.15,0:13:05.77,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,until it wanders into the hands of the next master.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.48,0:13:11.11,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Even then, it's better than having a huge disaster right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.39,0:13:12.58,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,I suppose so.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.25,0:13:43.62,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Were it possible, I would like to postpone our promised showdown.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.62,0:13:45.88,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,But you have higher speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.25,0:13:49.32,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,If I can't escape, I must fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.32,0:13:50.12,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.59,0:13:53.15,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,That is why I've come.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.20,0:14:37.50,Nanoha Device1,,0,0,0,,Snake Form
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.20,0:14:37.50,Nanoha Device2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(476,650)}Schlangenform
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.99,0:14:54.25,Nanoha Device1,,0,0,0,,Load Cartridge. Haken Form.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.66,0:15:01.49,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,{\b1}Haken Saber{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.41,0:15:14.57,Nanoha Device1,,0,0,0,,Blitz Rush
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.26,0:15:28.59,Nanoha Device1,,0,0,0,,Haken Slash
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.96,0:15:34.22,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,The sheath!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.63,0:15:40.86,Nanoha Device1,,0,0,0,,Plasma Lancer
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.88,0:15:48.94,Nanoha Device1,,0,0,0,,Assault Form
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.35,0:15:55.72,Nanoha Device1,,0,0,0,,Sword Form
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.35,0:15:55.72,Nanoha Device2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(475,650)}Schwertform
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.36,0:16:10.53,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,{\b1}Plasma...{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.50,0:16:15.56,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,{\b1}Flying Dragon...{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.34,0:16:18.31,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,{\b1}...Smasher{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.44,0:16:23.41,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,{\b1}...Flash{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.44,0:16:54.34,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,If you're a familiar... a guardian beast... like me,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.84,0:16:59.08,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,shouldn't you be trying to correct your mistress' errors?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.08,0:17:02.38,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,We fill the Book of Darkness of our own will.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.65,0:17:08.62,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Our mistress has no knowledge of our filling of the pages.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.62,0:17:09.72,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.43,0:17:11.65,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,What does that...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.13,0:17:17.83,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Fighting for your mistress, even if blood stains your hands?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.83,0:17:23.33,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,As a fellow guardian beast like myself, would you not do so?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.91,0:17:26.34,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,I would!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.88,0:17:29.44,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,But, even so!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.69,0:17:39.55,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,Signum's group is...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.55,0:17:42.89,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,Yes... they're fighting in the desert now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.89,0:17:46.35,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,Against Testarossa and her guardian beast.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.43,0:17:50.53,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,It'll be bad if it goes on for too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.53,0:17:51.97,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,Should I go help her?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.54,0:18:03.68,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,Vita?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.68,0:18:06.78,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,Dammit... another one showed up over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.78,0:18:08.48,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,That girl in the white outfit...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.05,0:18:10.85,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,No-name Takamachi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.55,0:18:14.42,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,It's Nanoha, already!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.42,0:18:16.72,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Na-no-ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.43,0:18:21.60,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Vita...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.60,0:18:25.06,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Can't I hear what you have to say after all?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.73,0:18:27.57,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,You never know,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.57,0:18:32.47,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,it's possible that I can help you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.48,0:18:38.75,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.75,0:18:42.52,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,I can't trust anything that someone from the Bureau would say!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.52,0:18:46.08,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,I'm not from the Bureau.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.12,0:18:48.61,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,I'm just a civilian helper.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.76,0:18:55.80,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,I can only fill pages of the Book of Darkness once from any mage.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.80,0:18:59.93,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,In other words, even if I defeat her, she won't turn into new pages.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.47,0:19:04.13,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,I'd like to avoid wasting cartridges too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.61,0:19:06.63,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Vita...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.18,0:19:08.44,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,I'll defeat you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.58,0:19:10.94,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,...some other time!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.75,0:19:15.84,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Howl, Graf Eisen!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.15,0:19:17.62,Nanoha Device1,,0,0,0,,Iron Howl
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.15,0:19:17.62,Nanoha Device2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(477,650)}Eisengeheul
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.50,0:19:29.52,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Gotta escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.74,0:19:38.93,Nanoha Device1,,0,0,0,,Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.78,0:19:42.84,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.84,0:19:45.47,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,She can't attack me from that far away.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.08,0:19:48.61,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Dimensional transport...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.25,0:19:52.79,Nanoha Device1,,0,0,0,,Buster Mode
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.79,0:19:54.22,Nanoha Device1,,0,0,0,,Drive Ignition
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.53,0:19:59.59,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Here goes...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.59,0:20:01.96,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,My first long-range blaster attack in a while!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.66,0:20:03.96,Nanoha Device1,,0,0,0,,Load Cartridge
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.90,0:20:10.21,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.21,0:20:13.11,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,She's going to shoot?!\NFrom that far away?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.22,0:20:22.35,Nanoha Device1,,0,0,0,,Divine Buster...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.35,0:20:23.68,Nanoha Device1,,0,0,0,,...Extension
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.69,0:20:27.02,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,{\b1}Divine...{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.63,0:20:33.53,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,{\b1}...Buster{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.73,0:20:36.70,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,You're kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.13,0:20:48.66,Nanoha Device1,,0,0,0,,It's a direct hit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.84,0:20:51.88,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Did we overdo it a little?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.88,0:20:53.41,Nanoha Device1,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.59,0:21:06.06,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.06,0:21:07.60,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.60,0:21:11.16,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,You're going to finish the\NBook of Darkness, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.67,0:21:19.30,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,{\b1}Divine...{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.14,0:21:23.58,Nanoha Device1,,0,0,0,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.82,0:21:28.15,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,A bind?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.15,0:21:29.62,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,It can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.62,0:21:32.05,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,From all the way over there, in an instant?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.10,0:21:46.93,Nanoha Device1,,0,0,0,,Sorry, master.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.87,0:21:50.70,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,No... I was caught off guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.22,0:22:11.96,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,This far in the game, yet so fast...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.79,0:22:15.23,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,She's starting to make attacks my eyes can't keep up with.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.90,0:22:18.13,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,If I don't end this battle soon, it will go badly.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.27,0:22:27.67,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,So strong...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.81,0:22:32.08,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,She's overpowering me at both close-range and mid-range...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.71,0:22:35.12,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,For now, I'm fooling her with my speed,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.05,0:22:38.65,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,but if she lands a blow squarely, she'll crush me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.79,0:22:45.12,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,Will I be able to land a hit with Storm Falcon?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.79,0:22:45.12,Nanoha Device2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(769,107)}Sturmfalken
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.76,0:22:49.25,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,No choice but to use Sonic Form?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.25,0:23:12.74,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Testarossa!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.13,0:23:20.22,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Curse you!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.91,0:23:34.47,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Now, take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.29,0:23:40.46,Nanoha ED,,0,0,0,,I won't forget even when I grow up
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.46,0:23:48.39,Nanoha ED,,0,0,0,,My love, the day that we came across each other
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.04,0:23:53.17,Nanoha ED,,0,0,0,,In this place, where flowers bloom intensely
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.17,0:23:56.88,Nanoha ED,,0,0,0,,I kept you in tears
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.88,0:24:00.28,Nanoha ED,,0,0,0,,I remember the promise
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.28,0:24:06.74,Nanoha ED,,0,0,0,,My love, the smile that I love so much
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.79,0:24:17.39,Nanoha ED,,0,0,0,,That day, when the secret door opened
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.80,0:24:24.83,Nanoha ED,,0,0,0,,I was chasing after a small white butterfly
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.18,0:24:33.08,Nanoha ED,,0,0,0,,I got lost, and I wanted to cry
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.08,0:24:36.82,Nanoha ED,,0,0,0,,My true wishes, my true feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.82,0:24:41.32,Nanoha ED,,0,0,0,,Maybe you taught those to me
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.32,0:24:45.46,Nanoha ED,,0,0,0,,Guarded by such kind feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.46,0:24:49.03,Nanoha ED,,0,0,0,,I'm sure I was spoiled for all this time
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.03,0:24:52.83,Nanoha ED,,0,0,0,,How you thought dear of me
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.83,0:24:58.80,Nanoha ED,,0,0,0,,My love, I won't forget all of you
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.24,0:25:12.78,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,Fate's Linker Core has been taken.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.78,0:25:14.45,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,The {\i0}Arthra{\i1} is back,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.45,0:25:17.92,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,but the mysteries of the case grow even deeper.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.92,0:25:19.82,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,What is the history of the Book of Darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.82,0:25:21.88,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,that Yuuno's research uncovers?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.22,0:25:25.24,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,Next episode of\N{\i0}Magical Girl Lyrical Nanoha A's:{\i1}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.24,0:25:30.03,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,Episode 8: The Heartbreaking Decision\Nand the Courageous Choice
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.03,0:25:32.20,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,Drive Ignition!
